data.description: Looking for Your Own Private Oasis that sits on over 2 Acres of Land? This is the Perfect Property for You! Beautiful Ranch Style Home with 4 Big Bedrooms and a Spacious Layout. The best part of this house is the Huge Florida Room overlooking the Screened- In Ground Pool. The Oversized Pool has a NEW LINER, NEW TILE AND NEW STAIRS! You will never run out of Storage Space in this House. You have Two Separate Garages attached and Two Storage Sheds out Back! Plenty of Parking options for all of Your House Guests. This property includes a Mother-in-Law Suite that you could rent separately or create your own Unique Space. Truly this is a great home with Serene and Plenty of Privacy! Call Today to make this place Yours! Buyer to Verify Own Dimensions & Size.
